graph TD
  User((User Interface)) --> Frontend[Frontend Web/Mobile]
  Frontend --> Backend[Central Monolith Backend]
  
  subgraph Backend_Monolith [Internal Modules]
    Backend --> Auth[Authentication Module]
    Backend --> Match[Route Matching Module]
    Backend --> Pay[Payment Module]
    Backend --> Eco[Eco-Impact Tracker]
    Backend --> Notif[Notification Module]
    Backend --> UserMgmt[User Management]
  end
  
  Backend --> DB[(Central Database)]